CGI::Auth::Basic
===========

Basic CGI authentication interface.

Read the module's POD for documentation and examples.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or under Windows:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

See the resulting pictures from the tests for sample
graphics (if you "make test"). 

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires this other module:

	CGI
	Fcntl

Which are standard in perl distributions.

